Citation.sTitle: Vapor Liquid Equilibrium for Binary System of 2-Propanol + 2-Ethoxy-2-methylpropane and Ethyl Ethanoate + 2-Ethoxy-2-methylpropane at 333 K and 2-Propanone + 2-Ethoxy-2-methylpropane at 323 K
Citation.sAbstract: Isothermal vapor-liquid equilibrium was measured in range of pressures from 38.8 kPa to 82.1 kPa for 2-propanol + 2-ethoxy-2-methylpropane and ethyl ethanoate + 2-ethoxy-2-methylpropane at 333 K and 2-propanone + 2-ethoxy-2-methylpropane at 323 K with a circulation still. The liquid and condensed vapor phase samples were analyzed by a gas chromatograph. The experimental data was correlated with the Wilson activity coefficient model.
